OL,5,G2045 FIFA WC2026: Panama v England
OL,6,     FPanama v England (Kick-off
OL,7,     F10.00pm). Mark Pougatch presents
OL,8,     Fcoverage of the Group L match at
OL,9,     FNew York/New Jersey Stadium in the
OL,10,     FUSA, as the two sides play their
OL,11,     Ffinal group game. This is just the
OL,12,     Fsecond-ever meeting between the
OL,13,     Ftwo countries, with the first
OL,14,     Fcoming in the group stage of the
OL,15,     F2018 World Cup in Russia. That
OL,16,     Fgame was a memorable one for the
OL,17,     FThree Lions as they brushed their
OL,18,     Fopponents aside with a 6-1
OL,19,     Fvictory. Braces from Harry Kane
OL,20,     Fand John Stones, as well as a goal
OL,21,     Ffrom Jesse Lingard, gave England a
OL,22,     F5-0 lead at half-time before Kane
